trans-unit.source: Provides a component editor for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection"></xref> object in the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller en komponent redigerare för den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection"> </xref> objekt i den associerade <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"> </xref> kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor class provides a user interface for editing the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle> elements of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection> object in the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control at design time, under the control of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner> object.
trans-unit.target: Klassen SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor ger ett användargränssnitt för att redigera den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>element i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>objekt i den associerade <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroll vid designtillfället under kontroll av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner>objekt.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>

trans-unit.source: There is a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection> associated with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control.
trans-unit.target: Det finns en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>som är associerade med den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A>egenskapen för den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection> object is used to apply styles to static submenu items that depend on their level (nesting depth) in the menu structure.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>objektet används för att använda format statiska undermeny objekt som beror på nivån (inkapslingsdjup) i menyn struktur.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>

trans-unit.source: The SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor is invoked, for example, by selecting the ellipsis button (**…**) on the **LevelSubMenuStyles** row in the **Properties** grid of the visual designer.
trans-unit.target: SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor anropas, till exempel genom att välja knappen med tre punkter (**... **) på den **LevelSubMenuStyles** rad i den **egenskaper** rutnät av den visuella designern.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A> method always returns `false` to indicate that only one object can be selected at a time in the editor.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A>metoden returnerar alltid `false` som anger att endast ett objekt kan väljas i taget i redigeraren.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateCollectionForm%2A> method creates a new form to display and edit the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateCollectionForm%2A>Metoden skapar ett nytt formulär för att visa och redigera <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateCollectionForm%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateInstance%2A> method creates a new instance of the specified collection item type.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateInstance%2A>metoden skapar en ny instans av den angivna samling objekttypen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateInstance%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateNewItemTypes%2A> method returns an array of types that the editor can create.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateNewItemTypes%2A>metoden returnerar en matris av typer som kan skapa redigeraren.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateNewItemTypes%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor> class when you select, for example, the ellipsis button (**…**) on the **LevelSubMenuStyles** row in the **Properties** grid of the visual designer when designing a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control or a control that is derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> class.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework internt skapar en ny instans av klassen <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor>när du väljer, till exempel på ellipsknappen (**... **) på den **LevelSubMenuStyles** rad i den **egenskaper** rutnät av den visuella designern när du skapar en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroll eller en kontroll som härleds från <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>klassen</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> of the collection to edit.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Type>Mängden att redigera.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether multiple <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle"></xref> elements can be selected in the editor at one time.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar ett värde som anger om flera <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle"> </xref> element kan väljas i redigeraren i taget.

trans-unit.source: The CanSelectMultipleInstances method always returns `false`; thus, only one <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle> object can be selected at a time in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CanSelectMultipleInstances returnerar alltid `false`; därför bara en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>objekt kan väljas i taget i den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor>objekt.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>

trans-unit.source: Always <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Always <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.

trans-unit.target: En instans av den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CollectionEditor.CollectionForm>ska användas som den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor"> </xref>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CollectionEditor.CollectionForm>

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the specified collection item type.
trans-unit.target: Skapar en ny instans av den angivna samling objekttypen.

trans-unit.target: Metoden CreateInstance används för att skapa nya <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>objekt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>

trans-unit.target: CreateInstance-anrop i <xref:System.Activator.CreateInstance%2A>metod för att komma åt Aktiveringsmetoder för sent bundna support.</xref:System.Activator.CreateInstance%2A>

trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>för att skapa objektet.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.target: En ny instans av den angivna typen måste vara <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle"> </xref>.
